{"tid":1603782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[10.1] 只有齊上，沒有齊落","createTime":"2019-09-29T18:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T03:19:55.000Z","uid":40663,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f43e292e2738a6d1318b759b31622440ecd2b9dd","tid":1603782,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:25:51.000Z","msg":"給勇武：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">主攻唔守陣地，唔攻就轉場，多謝你地到今日仲肯企喺最前</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n給和理非：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再一窩蜂走，我地人數永遠比班狗多，要明白勇武冇晒，我地齊齊等死</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n給真香港人：<br />\n10月1，唔係最後一戰，但極為重要，可能係戰意最高昂嘅一日。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n祝各位武運昌隆<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e2q75h1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe2q75h1.jpg&h=a45da7df&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E0nFFRn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE0nFFRn.jpg&h=6222004f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/16vzLh2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F16vzLh2.jpg&h=b7d49d19&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZQP8PKH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZQP8PKH.jpg&h=c5e779b5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MNoYswo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMNoYswo.jpg&h=3dd49c21&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/74VcwX3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F74VcwX3.jpg&h=9048fbd1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mgw7kRo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmgw7kRo.jpg&h=30f28528&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mJxuzbs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmJxuzbs.png&h=88c49782&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e759b613259b7c8e3f69f303f2813d617171394","tid":1603782,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:26:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ae768c978d7fe571fb0a56db80d075139cccb11","tid":1603782,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:26:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"870ec5332a5dfe9435b0d34770401aa77bbc66f2","tid":1603782,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:26:58.000Z","msg":"推返轉頭，D狗仲驚過你啦<br />\n<br />\n［手足入］希望大家可以多D留意屋企樓下E個位，提防D奇怪人搵有用垃圾<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603671\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603671</a>"},{"pid":"96c13811759e0132dbd6aa762ce53cfba009a99d","tid":1603782,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:27:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5920a0fe6788600f6e9efd5a7593eda648229b2","tid":1603782,"uid":262997,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:29:32.000Z","msg":"推唔到但都想講，<br />\n<br />\n今日見到我地好多人，但班狗一從暗門走出來之後，我地就雞飛狗走，我明白，好多人連雞頭都未劈過，但冇架啦。<br />\n<br />\n再唔齊上，為我地行最前既人就只會有一日<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全部犧牲哂</span></span>，咁樣係我地想見到架咩？<br />\n<br />\n我地係時候要打最美一仗啦。"},{"pid":"4a790f05b89baa08863148730af27ec9bd13daf2","tid":1603782,"uid":314509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:30:57.000Z","msg":"封重生點！<br />\n和理非要有危機意識但唔好慌！<br />\n讀宣言！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zhwF7kd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzhwF7kd.jpg&h=5781479b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v40Ly0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv40Ly0d.jpg&h=3864b67f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">原po在此：<br />\n【重要行動/文宣】十一光復香港宣言<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1595334\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1595334</a></span>"},{"pid":"db40b55f00071375d45d0ddaaef76eee5aa220b3","tid":1603782,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:31:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1ee811a5f65f36d39c90788f91c6979515d81dd","tid":1603782,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:33:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24eef5d4ae062e9c473631b468c2adb0bc3eddc2","tid":1603782,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:33:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca9fb27b52753827771072f3d5e6e05855563de4","tid":1603782,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:34:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0382dbc50d6240714f8de7ffb8ad6a86fd3b1530","tid":1603782,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:36:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c740d4221dca71e238c54c2872fa15ce21ceeef2","tid":1603782,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:39:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f90054f6afc9fceeaff2063c4c13d3a0038c739","tid":1603782,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:02:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3c4e4f77bf50677a085583b106823106b87310a","tid":1603782,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:16:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0745ad39f90ddfa8b2d12b8b8a950b0d6e4b8186","tid":1603782,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:38:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20af9a9601fc36ab70b27cab7f5979c1203afaf2","tid":1603782,"uid":277540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T20:13:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/gymzacdon.hk/photos/a.1705717553057757/2151187005177474/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgymzacdon.hk%2Fphotos%2Fa.1705717553057757%2F2151187005177474%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26thea